  16. open Misc

  18. (* Link .cmo files and produce a bytecode executable. *)

  20. module Dep : Set.OrderedType with type t = modname * modname
  21. module DepSet : Set.S with type elt = Dep.t

  23. val link : filepath list -> filepath -> unit
  24. val reset : unit -> unit

  26. val check_consistency: filepath -> Cmo_format.compilation_unit -> unit

  28. val extract_crc_interfaces: unit -> crcs

  30. type error =
  31.   | File_not_found of filepath
  32.   | Not_an_object_file of filepath
  33.   | Wrong_object_name of filepath
  34.   | Symbol_error of filepath * Symtable.error
  35.   | Inconsistent_import of modname * filepath * filepath
  36.   | Custom_runtime
  37.   | File_exists of filepath
  38.   | Cannot_open_dll of filepath
  39.   | Required_module_unavailable of modname * modname
  40.   | Camlheader of string * filepath
  41.   | Wrong_link_order of DepSet.t
  42.   | Multiple_definition of modname * filepath * filepath

  44. exception Error of error

  46. open Format

  48. val report_error: formatter -> error -> unit
